      "Sagittarius's constitution is generally robust — Jupiter's influence gives them a natural vitality, resilience, and recuperative power that keeps them bouncing back from illness and injury with impressive speed. They tend toward an active lifestyle naturally, which supports their cardiovascular health and maintains their energy levels well into later life. Their warm, extroverted nature supports their mental health through social connection and an optimism that acts as a buffer against the worst effects of stress. However, Jupiter's influence also creates a tendency toward excess that can undermine their physical wellbeing — too much food, too much drink, too much activity without adequate rest.",

